[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "波も穏やかだし、ベスティラまで\n問題なく行けるといいな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00698",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "この辺りは監察局本部のお膝元だし、\n海賊なんかも滅多に出ないはずだけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00699",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "気になるのはベスティラに着いた後のことだよね。\nさっき聞いた話だと現地である事件が起きてるらしくて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00700",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ある事件？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00701",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "なんでも若い獣人の女の子が連続で消えたとか……\nエルスさんたちの目的もこの事件の捜査だと思う",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00702",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "若い獣人の女の子……イザナちゃんをそんな危険な所に\n連れていけないよ！　バーバラ号に残ろう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00703",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "アタシは大丈夫、レスナちゃんの騎士だもん！\nもし怪しい奴に誘拐されそうになっても……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00704",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "このハンマーの錆にしてくれちゃうんだから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00705",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "頼もしい……けど、やっぱり心配だよ。\nずーっとイザナちゃんにくっついてよっと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00706",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "相変わらずの仲良しぶりですわね。\nもう１つの船に乗ったほうがよかったかしら",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_036_00707",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "ララは器用だね。\n揺れるのに、お茶を１滴もこぼさないもん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00708",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "王としてのたしなみ、というものですわ。\nいついかなる時も優雅に、美しく……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_036_00709",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "でも、ララさんまで\nついてきてくださって、嬉しいです！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00710",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "九偉人が「管理」と称してクリセルダを狙うのならば\n明日は我が身ですもの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_036_00711",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ララ・キングダムに危害が及ばぬよう、\n王自ら前線に出て、何かあれば決着を付けるのです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_036_00712",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "おおぅ、なんとも攻撃型の王っすね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00713",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "それにジェロンも一度やられたようですし、\nかつての戦友の危機に駆け付けないでどうしますか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_036_00714",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "わたくしが見事、ジェロンの仇を討ってみせますわ。\n彼も草葉の陰で喜んでくれることでしょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_036_00715",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "勝手に殺すな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00716",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（みんな、強敵の話を聞いても怯まない……\n　やっぱすごいな……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00717",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（アタシも、特訓をして前には進めた。\n　でもヘルトたちを見て、ビビッちゃってた）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00718",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（もっとだ。もっと自信をつける必要がある）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00719",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（アタシなりの、何かすごい一芸を習得しなくちゃ。\n　錬金術士で案内人の、アタシだからこその……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00720",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "姉様が、すごく思考している……ごくり",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_036_00721",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]